summary: A basic file to get all 10 Treasure Maps from the Vanilla Game.
descriptionHtml:
A basic file to get all 10 Treasure Maps from the Vanilla Game.
Instead of having to search for all of the maps, and then search for the chests, this cuts out the first part so you can get to finding those chests!


Install;
Unrar
place tmaps.txt file into your Skyrim\'s Data Folder
open console commands in-game
type bat tmaps

Good Luck!
author: Renoisnotking
